2229  C6BC D1               pop de
2230  C6BD E1               pop hl
2231  C6BE C9               ret
2232  C6BF
2233  C6BF              ; IsSolid — A=tile_id → Z=passable (AIR or FLAG), NZ=solid, A preserved
2234  C6BF              ; Fix 37: removed 'ld a,1 / or a' at end — cp TILE_FLAG already leaves Z clear
2235  C6BF              ; (NZ) for any non-FLAG solid tile, and A is preserved so CheckCeiling can
2236  C6BF              ; read the tile_id back for QBlock detection without re-calling GetTileAt.
2237  C6BF              IsSolid:
