2560  C876
2561  C876                  ; Step 3: add signed vx (B) to IX using 16-bit arithmetic
2562  C876                  ; Sign-extend: if B bit7 set → negative, high extension = $FF; else $00
2563  C876 DD 7D            ld a, ixl
2564  C878 80               add a, b            ; low byte: IXL + vx (sets carry)
